title: DDFP 265: All-AFC South team & Titans Taylor Lewan
itunes:title: DDFP 265: All-AFC South team & Titans Taylor Lewan
description:
Shek & Rank are joined by "NFL Fantasy Live" analyst Marcas to help draft the All-AFC South team. Shek also tells tales of his Los Angeles clubbing nights with Prince and Ben Afflect. Lastly, Tennessee Titans rookie offensive lineman Taylor Lewan joins the show and picks favorites between Canada and Mexico.
